 ***bold_italics*** _**bold_italics**_ ___bold_italics___
 sub~script~ super^script^ ~~strikethrough~~ 
Dashes -- and --- 
Three consecutive dots ... into an ellipsis  
Fractions (may not work on some platforms) 1/2 1/3 3/4  
There's no "proper" way to indent. You have to  
$\quad$ hack it. More ways are listed on [this stackoverflow post](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6046263/how-to-indent-a-few-lines-in-markdown-markup)

